qW BI (hy pRBU! ieqnIAW lMmIAW smwDIAW lw ky BI) mYQoN qyrw mu`l nhIN pY skdw (qyry brwbr dw mYN iksy hor nUM l`B nhIN skdw), mYN qyrI ikqnI ku vifAweI d`sW? (mYN qyrI vifAweI d`sx jogw nhIN hW) ]1]
sdw kwiem rihx vwlw inr-Awkwr prmwqmw Awpxy Awp ivc itikAw hoieAw hY (aus nUM iksy hor dy Awsry dI muQwjI nhIN hY)
AsIN jIv iek dUjy qoN sux sux ky hI (aus dI bzurgI dw) ibAwn kr dyNdy hW[ (pr ieh koeI nhIN d`s skdw ik auh ikqnw ku v`fw hY)[ jy pRBU nUM cMgw l`gy qW (jIv dy AMdr AwpxI is&q-swlwh dI) qWG pYdw kr dyNdw hY ]1] rhwau]
